Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.390 --> 00:00:05.270
Ilovalarimizdagi "Res values" papkasida 
styles.xml faylini o‘zgartiramiz.

00:00:05.270 --> 00:00:08.470
"HeaderTextStyle" deb nomlangan 
ushbu uslubni qo‘shdik.

00:00:08.470 --> 00:00:11.760
Unda viktorinada ko‘rsatilgan 
beshta xususiyat mavjud.

00:00:11.760 --> 00:00:15.010
Bu matn ko‘rinishi uchun 
atribut nomi va bu qiymat.

00:00:16.030 --> 00:00:20.150
Keyin ushbu faoliyat uslubi 
uchun faoliyatning asosiy maket 

00:00:20.150 --> 00:00:20.980
faylida sarlavhadagi barcha matn 
ko‘rinishini o‘zgartirishimiz mumkin.

00:00:20.980 --> 00:00:25.687
style = "@ style / HeaderTextStyle" ni 
belgilaymiz.

00:00:25.687 --> 00:00:28.290
Va bu saralashning 
sarlavhasi hisoblanadi.

00:00:28.290 --> 00:00:30.990
miqdor sarlavhasi uchun 
xuddi shu narsani qilamiz.

00:00:30.990 --> 00:00:33.905
Endi, agar har doim sarlavhalar bizning ilovada qanday ko‘rinishini o‘zgartirishni xohlasak.

00:00:33.905 --> 00:00:36.135
Faqat bitta joyda 
yangilashimiz mumkin.

00:00:36.135 --> 00:00:39.405
Ilovani ishga tushirganimizda, barcha sarlavhalar bir xil bo‘lishini tekshirishimiz mumkin.

00:00:39.405 --> 00:00:40.775
Ilova ajoyib ko‘rinadi.

00:00:40.775 --> 00:00:43.025
Endi yana bir marta 
o‘zgartirish kiritishimiz kerak,

00:00:43.025 --> 00:00:45.665
va bu dastur mavzusi 
uchun ranglarni tanlashdan iborat bo‘ladi.

